oai_dc:dc.dc:description: ONE OF OUR BEAUTIFUL HOMES BUILT IN BUFF STONE AND WHITE BRICK. If you are going to Build anywhere North or South, write to us for information regarding plans, or send for our books: ARTISTIC HOMES, how to plan and how to build them. Filled with designs and plans, and much valuable information on building. Price, 25c. HOUSES AND BARNS. Book of low cost houses. Price, 50c. MODERN DWELLINGS.
